Maintainer: Rachel Carroll <rachelcarroll4@gmail.com>
Description: Performs Bayesian Improved Surname Geocoding (BISG) analysis to
  obtain probabilistic estimates of race based on surname and geolocation.   
  This package can be used in tandem with the 'eiCompare' package.
  Methods implemented in this package are described in Decter-Frain, 
  A., Sachdeva, P., Collingwood, L., Burke, J.,  Murayama, H., 
  Barreto, M., â€¦ Zingher, J. (2022). "Comparing Methods for Estimating 
  Demographics in Racially Polarized Voting Analyses" <doi:10.31235/osf.io/e854z>.
